        "name": "Who is Happy Roof?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Happy Roof LLC is a locally owned roofing contractor based in Oldsmar, Florida, serving Tampa Bay's Hillsborough, Pinellas, and Pasco counties. Founded in 2025 by a team with 30+ years of combined roofing experience, Happy Roof specializes in residential and commercial roof replacement, repair, storm damage restoration, and inspections. Florida License #CCC1337380." }
