      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. Happy Roof LLC is a fully licensed Florida roofing contractor (License #CCC1337380), bonded, and insured. We serve all of Hillsborough, Pinellas, and Pasco Counties." }
