      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Happy Roof installs Owens Corning asphalt shingles, Owens Corning shingles, Verea clay tile, concrete tile, and metal roofing. We help you choose the best option for Florida's climate and your budget." }
